 border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color=
: #ccc;"> wrote earlier this month</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">In like five years, technology =E2=
=80=94 and the SEC=E2=80=99s interpretation of the rules =E2=80=94 will hav=
e advanced to the point that banks will get fined if their bankers talk abo=
ut business with clients on the golf course. =E2=80=9CYou should have been =
wearing your bank-issued virtual reality headset and recorded the conversat=
ion,=E2=80=9D the SEC will say, or I guess =E2=80=9Cyou should have played =
golf in your bank=E2=80=99s official metaverse, which records all golf conv=
ersations for compliance review, rather than on a physical golf course.=E2=
=80=9D The golf course is an unofficial channel! No business allowed!</p></=
blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Well, similarly. If you want to get advice fro=
m a robot about how to invest =E2=80=94=C2=A0or if you want the robot to he=
lp you write a presentation for clients =E2=80=94=C2=A0then you had better =
communicate with the robot using official channels! Typing in the ChatGPT b=
ox isn=E2=80=99t an official channel, so it's not allowed.</p>
